<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV9">
<l>tiṇpūñ cuṭarnuti nēmiyañ celvarviṇ ṇāṭaṉaiya</l>
<l>vaṇpū maṇivalli yārē piripavar tāmivaiyō</l>
<l>kaṇpūṅ kamalaṅ karuñcuṭa rāṭiveṇ muttarumpi</l>
<l>vaṇpūṅ kuvaḷai maṭamāṉ viḻikkiṉṟa māyitaḻē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The sapphire creeper with flowers generous as the land of heaven</l>
<l>of the lord with the discus with firm, sharp, glowing rim, who will leave [her]?</l>
<l>As for these, eyes, flowering lotuses quivering with dark fire, white pearls budding,</l> 
<l>[are they] liberally flowering water-lilies, opened with huge petals by an innocent deer?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
